nodes.text: Brine Eyes-Li was a male Gran hitman from Malastare who served the RavinsBlud Crime Syndicate and Sebolto during the waning years of the Republic Classic era.

In 32 BBY, Brine was the originator of the bounty on the head of Meen Burtak. The Pixelito Grand Council posted a bounty on Li himself, 5000 credits alive, 2500 dead, that was collected by Jango Fett.
